is broadcasting a GIN contained in an entry of one of the "credentials holder controlled prioritized list of preferred GINs for access for localized services in SNPN" and whether the validity information of the entry is met and whether an available SNPNs are present in a list of "temporarily forbidden SNPNs for access for localized services in SNPN" or a list of "permanently forbidden SNPNs for access for localized services in SNPN" for an entry of the "list of subscriber data" or the PLMN subscription.
a)	SNPNs with the following order:
