ii)	the PLMN subscription shall be considered as selected, if the "credentials holder controlled prioritized list of preferred SNPNs for access for localized services in SNPN" associated with the PLMN subscription includes the SNPN identity of the selected SNPN and validity information of the selected SNPN in the "credentials holder controlled prioritized list of preferred SNPNs for access for localized services in SNPN" that includes the SNPN identity of the selected SNPN is not met;
-	for bullet a) 4) above:
